headline: Gap, Macy’s and Target Shares Plummet
summary: Shares of Gap, Macy's and Target nosedived Thursday on news of President Trump's latest round of tariffs. The new tariffs heavily penalize goods imported from Asia, where many retailers manufacture and source their products.
